Package: clocker
Type: Package
Title: Unified Epigenetic Clock Calculator
Version: 2.2.0
Authors@R: person("Kris", "[Last]", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "you@example.com")
Description: A unified interface for calculating 40+ epigenetic aging clocks
    from DNA methylation data. Handles raw IDAT files (via SeSAMe) and
    pre-processed beta matrices, including EPICv2 array support. Includes
    kNN imputation, methylQC-style sex inference, EpiDISH cell composition,
    and consolidated output for clocks across the literature (Horvath,
    Hannum, PhenoAge, GrimAge, DunedinPACE, PC-Clocks, epiTOC2, methylCIPHER
    family, and others).
